what are some nice ideas to show case my collections so we've got a game room now and i wanna show off all our collections what are some nice ideas to do so we have shelves book shelfs curios how do i display ornaments any ideas dont want them looking like there on an xmas tree i like the cup hook idea i have a lot of the old ornaments my mother and grandmother used and i just arranged them in a large clear glass bowl the main thing with collections is to keep all like items together arranging silver or crystal on pieces of mirror is pretty and adds depth just don't overdo it if you have lots and lots keep some packed away and rotate every so often Glass Sampling (music) The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time weapons and items RuneScape quests Wallpaper group Japanese tea ceremony Link (Legend of Zelda) Marilyn Monroe Aquarium Red Hot Chili Peppers Theory of conduct Filigree Extreme Programming The Sims 2 Star Trek Customizable Card Game RuneScape Mini-Games Ages of Myst Roxette Time Out of Mind Tea Stanley Cup Mid-levels House of Leaves Wood carving Animal Crossing Viva La Bam The Emancipation of Mimi Little Britain Arianne Diablo II British Library Self Portrait Castlevania: Harmony of Dissonance Solar cell Watch Telescope Wilton House Microeconomics Mirror Diablo II: Lord of Destruction RuneScape Bong Amateur telescope making Carbon dioxide sink The Sims 2: Nightlife Billboard (advertising) McFly Library Yu-Gi-Oh! Trading Card Game World of Warcraft Quake III Arena Ages of Uru Fischer Random Chess Pinball Neil Gaiman Milton H. Erickson Tetris Francis Bacon (painter) Geology of the Moon Migration Period art Petz Metroid Prime 2: Echoes Pok__mon (video games) Sonic the Hedgehog 2 Final Fantasy: Crystal Chronicles Yohoho! Puzzle Pirates My Little Pony Taxi Driver Pok__mon Crystal Chatsworth House Point groups in three dimensions The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Lathe Rainbow Islands Chicken CPU cache The Legend of Zelda: The Wind Waker The Time Machine Thermal pow